\c 8
\s Inzalo kaBhenjamini
\p
\v 1 UBhenjamini wasezala uBhela izibulo lakhe, uAshibeli owesibili\x + 7.6. Gen. 46.21. Nani 26.38.\x*, loAhara owesithathu\x + 7.12.\x*,
\v 2 uNoha owesine, loRafa owesihlanu.
\v 3 Njalo uBhela wayelamadodana: OAdari loGera loAbhihudi\x + Nani 26.40.\x*
\v 4 loAbishuwa loNamani\x + Nani 26.40.\x* loAhowa\x + 2 Sam. 23.28.\x*
\v 5 loGera loShefufani loHuramu.
\v 6 Lala ngamadodana kaEhudi; lezi zinhloko zaboyise zabahlali beGeba\x + Josh. 18.24.\x*; wasebathumbela eManahathi\x + 2.52,54.\x*;
\v 7 loNamani\x + 8.4,5.\x*, loAhiya\x + 8.4,5.\x*, loGera\x + 8.4,5.\x*; yena wabathumba; wasezala oUza loAhihudi.
\v 8 UShaharayimi wasezala \add abantwana\add* elizweni lakoMowabi, esebaxotshile; oHushimi loBahara babengomkakhe.
\v 9 Wasezala kuHodeshi umkakhe oJobabi loZibiya loMesha loMalikamu
\v 10 loJewuzi loSakiya loMirima. Laba babengamadodana akhe, izinhloko zaboyise.
\v 11 KuHushimi wasezala oAbitubi loEliphahali.
\v 12 Amadodana kaEliphahali: OEberi, loMishamu, loShemedi owakha iOno\x + Neh. 6.2.\x*\x + Ezra 2.33. Neh. 7.37. 11.35.\x* leLodi lemizana yayo\x + Seb. 9.32,35,38.\x*\x + Ezra 2.33. Neh. 7.37. 11.35.\x*\x + Neh. 6.2.\x*,
\v 13 loBeriya, loShema\x + 8.21.\x*, ababezinhloko zaboyise zabahlali beAjaloni\x + Josh. 10.12. Josh. 19.42.\x*, ababexotshe abahlali beGathi\x + 1 Sam. 17.4.\x*,
\v 14 loAhiyo, uShashaki, loJeremothi,
\v 15 loZebhadiya, loAradi, loEderi,
\v 16 loMikayeli, loIshipa, loJoha, amadodana kaBeriya\x + 8.13.\x*.
\v 17 LoZebhadiya, loMeshulamu, loHiziki, loHeberi,
\v 18 loIshmerayi, loIziliya, loJobabi, amadodana kaEliphahali\x + 8.12.\x*.
\v 19 LoJakimi, loZikiri, loZabidi,
\v 20 loEliyenayi, loZilethayi, loEliyeli,
\v 21 loAdaya, loBeraya, loShimirathi, amadodana kaShimeyi.
\v 22 LoIshipani, loEberi, loEliyeli,
\v 23 loAbidoni, loZikiri, loHanani,
\v 24 loHananiya, loElamu, loAnithothiya,
\v 25 loIfideya, loPenuweli, amadodana kaShashaki\x + 8.14.\x*.
\v 26 LoShamisherayi, loShekariya, loAthaliya,
\v 27 loJahareshiya, loEliya, loZikiri, amadodana kaJerohamu.
\v 28 Laba babezinhloko zaboyise, izinhloko ngezizukulwana zabo; laba bahlala eJerusalema.
\s Inzalo kaSawuli
\p
\v 29 EGibeyoni\x + 9.35-38.\x* kwasekuhlala uyise kaGibeyoni; lebizo lomkakhe lalinguMahaka\x + Josh. 9.3.\x*.
\v 30 Lendodana yakhe, izibulo lakhe, nguAbhidoni, loZuri, loKishi, loBhali, loNadabi,
\v 31 loGedori, loAhiyo, loZekeri.
\v 32 UMikilothi wasezala uShimeya\x + 9.37.\x*. Lalaba babehlala maqondana labafowabo eJerusalema, kanye labafowabo.
\p
\v 33 UNeri\x + 9.39-44.\x* wasezala uKishi; uKishi wasezala uSawuli; uSawuli wasezala oJonathani loMaliki-Shuwa\x + 1 Sam. 9.1. 14.51.\x* loAbinadaba loEshibhali\x + 10.2. 1 Sam. 31.2.\x*.
\v 34 Njalo indodana kaJonathani yayinguMeribi-Bhali; uMeribi-Bhali wasezala uMika\x + 2 Sam. 9.12.\x*.
\v 35 Njalo amadodana kaMika: OPithoni loMeleki loTareya loAhazi.
\v 36 UAhazi wasezala uJehoyada; uJehoyada wasezala oAlemethi loAzimavethi loZimri; uZimri wasezala uMoza;
\v 37 uMoza wasezala uBineya; uRafa \add wayey\add*indodana yakhe, uEleyasa indodana yakhe, uAzeli indodana yakhe.
\v 38 Njalo uAzeli wayelamadodana ayisithupha; lala ngamabizo awo: OAzirikamu, uBhokeru, loIshmayeli, loSheyariya, loObhadiya, loHanani. Wonke la ngamadodana kaAzeli.
\v 39 Njalo amadodana kaEsheki umfowabo: OUlamu izibulo lakhe, uJewushi eyesibili, loElifeleti eyesithathu.
\v 40 Njalo amadodana kaUlamu ayengamadoda, amaqhawe alamandla, anyathela idandili, elamadodana amanengi lamadodana amadodana, ikhulu lamatshumi amahlanu. Bonke laba babengabantwana bakoBhenjamini\x + 5.18.\x*.